Class Paper

java.lang.Object
edu.ufp.inf.paper_author.Paper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
PaperConference, PaperJournal
public class Paper extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a research paper with various attributes such as DOI, title, keywords, abstract, date, and metrics.
